== Tinker Design
- Layout selector like codpen
- Autorun as an option
- Multiple panes
  - Input and output
- Makefile-esque update
- Show errors in red output
- Docker to run code
- Terminal/shell view
- Key bindings
  - Ctrl keys to switch panes
